{"tid":1066244,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"完美接軌? 中環站疑列車相撞 港鐵：早上服務可能受影響","createTime":"2019-03-17T20:06:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-17T22:10:03.000Z","uid":141060,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a7f263656e7678db7e1a638bd7124c7ac494d26c","tid":1066244,"uid":141060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T20:06:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190318/large/1552852193_5243.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190318%2Flarge%2F1552852193_5243.jpg&h=88f9b907&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n凌晨約3時，港鐵荃灣綫中環站據報有列車相撞，一車長曾經被困，要由消防救出，另一車長腳部受傷。<br />\n港鐵表示，荃灣綫列車於今晨約3時、在中環站附近發生事故，早上服務可能受影響。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190318/59380446\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190318%2F59380446&d=0ENX7tHwQhT09cvOu3%2F4My9NcCfN%2BV0%2B2kMkFhSspzA%3D&h=af1b2a0b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190318%2F59380446&h=f261c83d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190318/59380446</a>"},{"pid":"ae427b2474eae73ec2c26481278122b9c3fddf9a","tid":1066244,"uid":191815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T20:08:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NxwSj5x.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNxwSj5x.png&h=2eaef901&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n心諗4點幾做咩有推送通知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec223f566270e12101ded9f3c03329397a3a3a41","tid":1066244,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T20:51:02.000Z","msg":"支那化"},{"pid":"46c92b55145a3db368b77dfca7209bdeb8ab9911","tid":1066244,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0